Title: The Calusari
Plot: The suspicious circumstances of a toddler's death leads Mulder and Scully into a Romanian exorcism ritual involving a young boy possessed by his stillborn twin.
GuestStars: Helene Clarkson, Joel Palmer, Lilyan Chauvin, Ric Reid, Bill Dow, Oliver Wildsmith, Jeremy Issac Wildsmith, Christine Willes, Kay E. Kuter, Jacqueline Danieneau, Bill Croft, George Josef, Campbell Lane
